These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, blood-red
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, lily
City: paris, marseilles
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who growslily##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |
| Color    | blood-red   | chestnut        |
| Beverage   | tea    | lemonade |
| Flower     | lily  | azalea       |
| City     | paris   | marseilles         |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary      |

