.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, mexican
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, coral
City: liverpool, hannover
2 different games are played: backgammon, poker
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, cain
1. the indian is on the left of the mexican##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is not to the right of the person playing poker##8
4. the person who likes coral is on the left of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Nationality         | indian   | mexican |
| Color   | coral  | yellow     |
| City   | liverpool  | hannover        |
| Game           | backgammon     | poker       |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | cain     |

