The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, rowing
1. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5
2. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person traveling to london##8
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |
